#&quot;The Coolest Guy in the World&quot; - 4:32
#&quot;My Guitar Wants to Kill Your Mama&quot; (Frank Zappa) - 4:11
#&quot;Comfort of Strangers&quot; - 4:11
#&quot;Bang Your Groove Thang&quot; - 3:35
#&quot;Your Money or Your Life&quot; - 4:14
