*&quot;Shalador&#x27;s Lady&quot;, March 2010 (Sequel to &quot;The Shadow Queen&quot;)
* &quot;Twilight&#x27;s Dawn&quot;, March 2011, collection of four Black Jewels stories:
** &quot;Winsol Gifts&quot;
** &quot;Shades of Honor&quot;
** &quot;Family&quot;
** &quot;The High Lord&#x27;s Daughter&quot;
* &quot;The Queen&#x27;s Bargain&quot;, March 2020
